'''小傑克·威廉·亨特'''（{{lang-en|Jack William Hunter, Jr.}}；{{bd|1974年|6月1日}}）是[[美國|美國]]的一位[[廣播|廣播]]節目主持人<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.charlestoncitypaper.com/charleston/ArticleArchives?author=1072546 |title=Jack Hunter at the Charleston City Paper |accessdate=2016-11-14 |archive-date=2018-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180924114414/https://www.charlestoncitypaper.com/charleston/ArticleArchives?author=1072546 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、政治評論家和Rare.us的政治編輯。他也是美國聯邦參議員[[蘭德·保羅|蘭德·保羅]]的支持者<ref name=usatoday0609>{{cite news|last=Carroll|first=James R.|last2=Gerth|first2=Joseph|title=Rand Paul staffer expressed support for Lincoln assassination|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2013/07/09/rand-paul-staffer-southern-avenger/2502637/|newspaper=USA Today|date=June 9, 2013|accessdate=2016-11-14|archive-date=2021-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211227114958/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2013/07/09/rand-paul-staffer-southern-avenger/2502637/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在政治上的觀點經常被認為偏向自由意志主義和保守主義。

